It isn't just one of your stupid n00b games.<br>
You may think at first I'm as mad as a hatter,<br>
When I tell you, a char can have THREE DIFFERENT NAMES.<br>
First of all, there's the name that the player selects<br>
And carefully picks at the creation screen.<br>
This may be Irexes or Traelle or Zildrax --<br>
All of them good, proper fantasy names.<br>
There are whimsical names if you think they sound better,<br>
Some fun and clever and some, well, they're lame --<br>
Teapray for the former and Mezmaster the latter,<br>
But all of them are, well, quite useable names.<br>
Later (at twentieth level) the player<br>
Can pick out a SURNAME to add on some shine.<br>
Some are quite funny (Squishytoes, a halfling)<br>
And some just sound nifty, like Shintou Shinai.<br>
Above and beyond, there's still one name left over,<br>
One known to all of the server and 'board,<br>
And that is the name that others will give you,<br>
If horses you steal or you're just a 'tard.<br>
If ranting and raving and trolling you do,<br>
If scamming and spamming are your MO,<br>
A third name you'll be granted, you can't ever lose it,<br>
And it is a name, well, that EVERYONE knows.<br>
Though labels are many for this kind of person,<br>
Some of them vulgar and others quite mild,<br>
There's only one name that fits every player<br>
Who we'd rather see kicked off and exiled.<br>
And what is this name, now the board-lurkers ask,<br>
This one name which 'pon a loser is written?<br>
It's cutesy, yet coarse this word that I tell you,<br>
Three syllables only, this one word,<br>
FUCKMITTEN.<br>
<br>
(A bard, I'm not.) <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.lionking.org/~black/art/koscha/koscha-sig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
